data.description: Westend Single Level Rancher. 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom Hardwood Floors through out this property.Galley Kitchen with updated appliances and Quartz counter tops. Gas Hot water, Wood Fireplace and Heat/Cool combo built-in unit for climate control in every season. Centrally located in great proximity to Miles, Lewis and Clark, and West High schools. Spacious deck for gatherings, underground sprinklers, and a convenient detached 2-car garage.
